{"tid":1289212,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有時間 星期六日真係要多d同老豆老母飲茶食下飯","createTime":"2019-07-06T04:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T04:36:43.000Z","uid":136738,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b84d6b9ae50b2d29c69d26ea8efb7652ff40ca9c","tid":1289212,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:04:59.000Z","msg":"咁老母係一個政治冷感嘅港豬<br />\n每日最大嘅活動就係返工返工<br />\n癲到可以ot到一個禮拜返7日<br />\n平時唔理政治 由細到大唔參加立法會區議會選舉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日同老母飲茶 先意識到佢公民意識幾薄弱<br />\n雖然我成日同佢講我同同學d嘢<br />\n所以佢都支持學生用和平方式發聲<br />\n但當我同佢講制度內制度外嘅時候<br />\n我發現佢真係乜都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同佢講立法會入面小圈子嘅時候<br />\n佢竟然問我咩係功能組別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住我仲住佢同佢講左兩個幾鐘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能我地宜家嘅教育 小學常識 中學通識<br />\n令我地可以好細個就有呢d公民意識<br />\n但係原來反而唔少成人無呢d我地覺得係常識嘅嘢<br />\n真係唔怪得知點解d廢中咁容易比人洗腦<br />\n所以有時間做下孝子 得閒食下飯灌輸d公民意識或者普世價值比佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老母今日仲叫我得閒同佢講多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲問我如果真係投投邊個好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4deb7194b384797e1b76ca229ab8bb7285b1b8fc","tid":1289212,"uid":136738,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:06:19.000Z","msg":"佢今日仲話覺得tvb好偏頗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b50968cb9cb3bd8cebf259f6abcbc80261d252","tid":1289212,"uid":48358,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:08:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/01GfFkH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt